      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a mechanically sound example of the A80 platform, featuring the venerable 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged 3.0L inline-six mated to the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission. The sequential turbocharger system provides consistent boost pressure, and the factory Torsen limited-slip differential ensures optimal power delivery to the rear wheels. The chassis retains its original double-wishbone suspension configuration and four-piston opposed-caliper braking system. Well-maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity, this Supra offers the tactile engagement and high-revving performance synonymous with 90s JDM engineering. It presents in solid driver condition, showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, but remains structurally and mechanically robust.",
